==Current daytime schedule==
  â
The first broadcast of the day on NBC is ''[[Early Today]]'', an expansion of the ''Today'' franchise. ''Early Today'' features top news stories, weather, and sports. The ''[[Today (NBC program)|Today]]'' show airs at 7:00 am, featuring a mix of news, weather, interviews, and lifestyle reports. On the weekend, the children's block [[qubo]] airs usually from 10 AM to 1 PM. ''[[Days of our Lives]]'' is currently the only daytime drama that airs on NBC, starting usually at 1:00. ''[[NBC Nightly News]]'' airs at 6:30 in most markets.
  â   â
Schedule usually depends on the local NBC affiliate.
